The paper is about face recognition using deep learning, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the architecture of the neural network used for face recognition, which is a key aspect of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the speed of the algorithm, which could be considered under multimedia (cs.MM). The use of deep learning for face recognition is also a popular topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
